Laravel create this route
| Action        | URL              | Method | Controller |
| ------------- | ---------------- | ------ | ---------- |
| List posts    | /posts           | GET    | index()    |
| Show form     | /posts/create    | GET    | create()   |
| Save post     | /posts           | POST   | store()    |
| Show one post | /posts/{id}      | GET    | show()     |
| Edit form     | /posts/{id}/edit | GET    | edit()     |
| Update post   | /posts/{id}      | PUT    | update()   |
| Delete post   | /posts/{id}      | DELETE | destroy()  |

